1785420,"title":"Win 下大家用什么输入法？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/827232","created":1641779783,"deleted":0,"content":"我其实用了很长一段时间的 微软拼音，就是觉得他界面比较简单，且开箱即用，但是重装系统后发现了很多蛋疼的问题，比如：\r\n\r\n输入法默认模式配置为中文时，在 Edge 等软件默认还是英文模式（[网上查]( https://answers.microsoft.com/zh-hans/windows/forum/all/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E6%8B%BC%E9%9F%B3%E8%BE%93/cd008d0c-eb7b-4061-9fdd-03daffb10cfc)发现大家都在问这个问题，却没有解决办法）\r\n\r\n还有那个[使用左面语言栏（如果可用）]，这个如果可用就真的是很魔幻。\r\n\r\n感觉微软对这个输入法并不重视，因此想了解一下大家现在用的什么输入法，让我调研一下。","content_rendered":"<p>我其实用了很长一段时间的 微软拼音，就是觉得他界面比较简单，且开箱即用，但是重装系统后发现了很多蛋疼的问题，比如：</p>\n<p>输入法默认模式配置为中文时，在 Edge 等软件默认还是英文模式（<a href=\"https://answers.microsoft.com/zh-hans/windows/forum/all/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E6%8B%BC%E9%9F%B3%E8%BE%93/cd008d0c-eb7b-4061-9fdd-03daffb10cfc\" rel=\"nofollow\">网上查</a>发现大家都在问这个问题，却没有解决办法）</p>\n<p>还有那个[使用左面语言栏（如果可用）]，这个如果可用就真的是很魔幻。</p>\n<p>感觉微软对这个输入法并不重视，因此想了解一下大家现在用的什么输入法，让我调研一下。</p>\n","last_modified":1641779802,"replies":21,"id":827232},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1630643991","name":"iphone","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1630643991","title":"iPhone","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","topics":9136,"footer":"这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。","header":"Say hello to the future.","title_alternative":"iPhone","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991","stars":2794,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":8,"parent_node_name":"apple"},"member":{"id":550759,"username":"lyhang","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/lyhang","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/33cd/32d7/550759_mini.png?m=1626161724","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/33cd/32d7/550759_normal.png?m=1626161724","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/33cd/32d7/550759_large.png?m=1626161724","created":1626161595,"last_modified":1626161724},"last_reply_by":"so898","last_touched":16