口难道不供电吗，几个 type-A 的接口就可以传输数据和供电。看了英文的和中文的使用手册，对这几个 type-c 的描述稍微有点出入。type-A 都可以双功能，type-c 反而只能传输数据？","content_rendered":"<p>有谁知道这个拓展坞的  雷电 3 的一个接口，另外几个传输数据的 type-c 接口难道不供电吗，几个 type-A 的接口就可以传输数据和供电。看了英文的和中文的使用手册，对这几个 type-c 的描述稍微有点出入。type-A 都可以双功能，type-c 反而只能传输数据？</p>\n","last_modified":1641775953,"replies":8,"id":827211},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1641688451","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1641688451","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":47024,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1641688451","stars":7659,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":354931,"username":"aboat365","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/aboat365","website":"https://aboat365.com/","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8bd11beb5b34ac9aa904ad229e5679d?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8bd11beb5b34ac9aa904ad229e5679d?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8bd11beb5b34ac9aa904ad229e5679d?s=73&d=retro","created":1539135057,"last_modified":1539135057},"last_reply_by":"coderluan","last_touched":1641785466,"title":"开源，是否是一门生意？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/827256","created":1641784461,"deleted":0,"content":"Faker.js 删库事件有感。先声明本人是名普通程序员，偶尔维护开源项目，在工作中也使用大量的开源程序。天下熙熙皆为利来，天下攘攘皆为利往，如果站在利益（中性词）的角度来观察开源，就能看到不一样的世界。本人认为，开源就是一门生意，Faker.js 的作者只是一个生意失败的人。  \r\n纵观开源界，确实人才济济，有各种厉害的项目，但成功背后都有资本的影子。开源世界，并非是世外桃源，反而是一个毫无规则，毫无底线的修罗场。大多数的开源项目，就如同那河里的鹅卵石，随波逐流。漂亮的鹅卵石偶尔会被小孩子发现拾起，更多只是被捞起碾碎成了混凝土，大多数直接淹没在历史的断层里。  \r\n最后，我只是一个玩泥巴的人，希望有人一起来玩泥巴。","content_rendered":"<p>Faker.js 删库事件有感。先声明本人是名普通程序员，偶尔维护开源项目，在工作中也使用大量的开源程序。天下熙熙皆为利来，天下攘攘皆为利往，如果站在利益（中性词）的角度来观察开源，就能看到不一样的世界。本人认为，开源就是一门生意，Faker.js 的作者只是一个生意失败的人。<br/>\n纵观开源界，确实人才济济，有各种厉害的项目，但成功背后都有资本的影子。开源世界，并非是世外桃源，反而是一个毫无规则，毫无底线的修罗场。大多数的开源项目，就如同那河里的鹅卵石，随波逐流。漂亮的鹅卵石偶尔会被小孩子发现拾起，更多只是被捞起碾碎成了混凝土，大多数直接淹没在历史的断层里。<br/>\n最后，我只是一个玩泥巴的人，希望有人一起来玩泥巴。</p>\n","last_modified":1641784461,"replies":7,"id":827256},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e44f/ea3b/454_large.png?m=1571210070","name":"lol","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e44f/ea3b/454_normal.png?m=1571210070","title":"英雄联盟","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/lol","topics":341,"footer":"","header":"League of Legends (LoL) is a multiplayer online battle arena video game.","title_alternative":"League of Legends","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e44f/ea3b/454_mini.png?m=1571210070","stars":465,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":454,"parent_node_name":"games"},"member":{"id":170434,"username":"ChengLuffy","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ChengLuffy","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/753a/0be0/170434_mini.png?m=1469000234","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/753a/0be0/170434_normal.png?m=1469000234","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/753a/0be0/170434_large.png?m=1469000234","created":1461484612,"last_modified":1469000234},"last_reply_by":"Tiode","last_touched":1641785414,"title":"2022 年 LPL 比赛日历文件已更新","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/827250","created":1641783126,"deleted":0,"content":"前情提要 https://v2ex.com/t/683659#reply8\r\n\r\n\r\niPhone 用户可以在 设置 -> 密码和账户 -> 添加账户 -> 其他 -> 添加已订阅的日历\r\n\r\niOS 14 及以上在 设置 -> 日历 -> 账户...\r\n\r\nGithub 订阅源 https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ChengLuffy/lpl.ics/master/LPL2022.ics\r\n\r\n加入了日历提醒，会在比赛预订开始时间 5 分钟之前提醒，可以在 日历应用点击下面的日历，点击该订阅后的叹号，把日程提醒关了就不会有提醒。\r\n\r\n可以用作一个简单的数据查询使用。\r\n\r\nPreview\r\n---\r\n\r\n![IMG_0854]( https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15682381/85242547-e7b62700-b471-11ea-9d3b-fbeb27e733ff.PNG)\r\n![IMG_0855]( https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15682381/85242553-ea188100-b471-11ea-9d15-2bea61354a8f.PNG)","content_rendered":"<p>前情提要 <a href=\"https://v2ex.com/t/683659#reply8\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://v2ex.com/t/683659#reply8</a></p>\n<p>iPhone 用户可以在 设置 -&gt; 密码和账户 -&gt; 添加账户 -&gt; 其他 -&gt; 添加已订阅的日历</p>\n<p>iOS 14 及以上在 设置 -&gt; 日历 -&gt; 账户...</p>\n<p>Github 订阅源 <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ChengLuffy/lpl.ics/master/LPL2022.ics\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ChengLuffy/lpl.ics/master/LPL2022.ics</a></p>\n<p>加入了日历提醒，会在比赛预订开始时间 5 分钟之前提醒，可以在 日历应用点击下面的日历，点击该订阅后的叹号，把日程提醒关了就不会有提醒。</p>\n<p>可以用作一个简单的数据查询使用。</p>\n<h2>Preview</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"IMG_0854\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15682381/85242547-e7b62700-b471-11ea-9d3b-fbeb27e733ff.PNG\"/>\n<img alt=\"IMG_0855\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15682381/85242553-ea188100-b471-11ea-9d15-2bea61354a8f.PNG\"/></p>\n","last_modified":1641783126,"replies":7,"id":827250}]